history.content: <md>Figuring out what to do with your cancelled weekend plans? Interested in climate change? Right now there’s an invaluable opportunity to participate in a world-wide climate change hackathon tackling the problem of solar power production forecasts using machine learning! And — they're offering a $68k cash prize. To learn more, make sure to visit https://climatehack.ai and sign up. Submissions are due on March 16th.</md>
history.subject: ClimateHack AI Hackathon
